text: As it's my first time working with HubSpot, I am integrating HubSpot with my voip calling app(i have developed it myself) and i found some difficulties while integrating (in developing/making iframe for call widgets) . Is there anyone who have done this before or can help me out?

Has anyone noticed that there seems to be a bug(?) when trying to add a form module to e.g. footer.html.
It will show up fine in the preview, but once you publish the page and view it as a published page it will only display an email field, regardless of what you created with the form builder
<@U04BGQL6AGY> Not yet. Please send me the screenshot of it.

the `--assetVersion` flag is not working for cli `v4.1.7` . the line below only gets the old version across multiple portals (old and new)
```hs fetch @HubSpot/search_input.module --assetVersion=1```
also there is no documentation on the `--assetVersion` flag for <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/cms/developer-reference/local-development-cli#fetch|fetch>
